My treat.

48
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:40,590
- Huh? Is that okay?
- Yeah.

49
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,420
Ahem.

50
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:46,510
Thanks. I'll have the same.

51
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,860
Same for him!

52
00:03:52,541 --> 00:03:54,728
