so I was surprised.

80
00:07:06,066 --> 00:07:08,833
I'm glad you're not dead.

81
00:07:09,166 --> 00:07:11,866
I'll report you to the police.

82
00:07:12,860 --> 00:07:15,500
I remember your face.

83
00:07:30,766 --> 00:07:32,466
What? You're still alive, huh?

84
00:07:32,466 --> 00:07:34,460
You're going to kill me?

85
00:07:36,033 --> 00:07:38,066
This guy is so noisy.

86
00:07:39,366 --> 00:07:41,833
Are you going to kill me and bury me?

87
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,260
Kaji!

88
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,960
Sorry, sorry.

89
00:07:47,266 --> 00:07:49,400
Just threatening him a bit.

90
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:54,133
If he died, I'd be in trouble.

91
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:57,600
Here, drink some water.

92
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,151
You were leeching off someone

93
00:08:16,167 --> 00:08:18,010
living in a luxury tower in Azabu, right?

94
00:08:18,934 --> 00:08:20,572
You got caught fooling around

95
00:08:20,612 --> 00:08:22,510
with other guys and got kicked out.

96
00:08:23,133 --> 00:08:24,484
You stole a card when you left,

97
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,500
didn't you?

98
00:08:25,733 --> 00:08:27,900
Do you understand what you did?

99
00:08:30,766 --> 00:08:32,366
Get out.

100
00:08:56,833 --> 00:08:59,133
The credit card got blocked immediately!

101
00:08:59,333 --> 00:09:01,800
- I didn't take cash either.
- That's not it.

102
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:04,600
There was another card. The black one.

103
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:07,080
I thought it was a black card,

104
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,533
but it wasn't a credit card,

105
00:09:08,557 --> 00:09:10,267
so I just tossed it somewhere!

106
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:12,660
Tossed it? Where?

107
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:14,533
In some convenience store's trash bin!

108
00:09:16,766 --> 00:09:19,466
Well, then it's gone for good.

109
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:24,266
I searched your whole body in the hotel.

110
00:09:24,633 --> 00:09:27,000
When I couldn't find it, I dumped you.

111
00:09:27,733 --> 00:09:28,959
But then I realized,

112
00:09:28,967 --> 00:09:31,576
I haven't asked him yet.

113
00:09:33,533 --> 00:09:36,233
So you just wanted the card back?

114
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,039
It's fine now.

115
00:09:39,710 --> 00:09:41,600
If you tossed it, nothing we can do.

116
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,200
Sorry for beating you up.

117
00:09:45,671 --> 00:09:47,366
Now disappear.

118
00:09:52,266 --> 00:09:54,600
