119
00:09:59,066 --> 00:10:00,866
Let me do it.

120
00:10:02,666 --> 00:10:05,000
We were in the middle of it.

121
00:10:05,966 --> 00:10:08,000
Let me finish!

122
00:10:10,133 --> 00:10:13,233
Is it here? Or maybe this way?

123
00:10:13,733 --> 00:10:18,266
- This is...
- We're moving.

124
00:10:20,100 --> 00:10:23,033
If you help us, I'll let you do it.

125
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,200
Huh?

126
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:26,292
Whether you do it or not, I don't care.

127
00:10:26,324 --> 00:10:28,230
Just be careful.

128
00:10:29,433 --> 00:10:32,200
You're a leech, right?

129
00:10:32,666 --> 00:10:34,376
You kept threatening like that,

130
00:10:34,385 --> 00:10:35,619
you're trash, huh?

131
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:39,233
And what about you guys?

132
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:41,142
We're scouts.

133
00:10:41,174 --> 00:10:42,814
For hostesses and sex workers.

134
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,133
Scouts?

135
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:48,233
That's a trash job too.

136
00:10:48,666 --> 00:10:50,142
You make money by making

137
00:10:50,167 --> 00:10:51,847
girls sell their bodies.

138
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,642
Even if I'm a trash,

139
00:10:53,658 --> 00:10:55,009
I'm still better than that.

140
00:10:56,966 --> 00:10:58,400
So what?

141
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,266
Nothing.

142
00:11:09,584 --> 00:11:10,702
Got beaten up like that

143
00:11:10,727 --> 00:11:11,736
and still want to do it?

144
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:14,800
No, even I don't understand.

145
00:11:16,060 --> 00:11:19,700
It can't be helped. My life is garbage.

146
00:11:21,433 --> 00:11:24,733
I thought I raised you right.

147
00:11:26,233 --> 00:11:28,900
Get out! You piece of trash!

148
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:38,080
Alright, move over a bit. Good.

149
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:40,033
- I said move it closer.
- Yes.

150
00:11:40,033 --> 00:11:42,030
Good. Ah. Excellent.

151
00:11:42,030 --> 00:11:44,500
You're in the shot, you idiot!

152
00:11:45,733 --> 00:11:49,200
Enough, will you? Die!

153
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:57,280
Life is garbage.

154
00:11:58,260 --> 00:11:59,540
But...

155
00:12:01,887 --> 00:12:03,062
There was something

156
00:12:03,078 --> 00:12:04,366
in his eyes last night.

157
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:08,109
A fragment of something

158
00:12:08,134 --> 00:12:09,701
that's not garbage.

159
00:12:19,180 --> 00:12:25,100
(BBQ Shop)

160
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,900
Haa...

161
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:39,240
Are you done?

162
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,420
Well, that was the last box.

163
00:12:42,340 --> 00:12:44,620
Alright, take care of the rest.

164
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,180
Wait...

165
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:55,300
Hey!

166
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,720
Alright.

167
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,920
I'm going to grab a coffee.

168
00:13:23,580 --> 00:13:24,920
Hey!

169
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:30,940
Damn it, I can't do this!

170
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,440
Hey,

171
00:14:29,540 --> 00:14:31,157
