173
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:36,880
- Hurry and clean up.
- Yeah, yeah. I'm working on it.

174
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:40,880
- Where's mine?
- There isn't any.

175
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:48,483
Life is like a box of chocolates.

176
00:14:49,186 --> 00:14:50,912
When I opened it, it was empty.

177
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:55,040
But even so, I couldn't give up.

178
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:58,220
I was searching for something.

179
00:15:11,820 --> 00:15:13,180
No need for that area.

180
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:14,890
We'll be moving again

181
00:15:14,915 --> 00:15:15,915
