182
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:17,890
Moving again?

183
00:15:18,054 --> 00:15:19,476
You just moved, didn't you?

184
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:23,740
It's fine. Take a break.

185
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,460
Where were you before this place?

186
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:33,960
Shinjuku.

187
00:15:34,940 --> 00:15:36,920
