188
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:39,500
My workplace is nearby.

189
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:42,260
Ah, the scouting job.

190
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:45,500
But this place is really run-down.

191
00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:48,340
There are many reasons.

192
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,000
It's just that you don't have any money.

193
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:51,539
If you're going to smoke,

194
00:15:51,570 --> 00:15:52,976
