195
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,000
Yeah.

196
00:16:01,620 --> 00:16:02,700
Haa...

197
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:06,620
You seem different

198
00:16:06,636 --> 00:16:08,316
from my first impression.

199
00:16:08,780 --> 00:16:10,120
You're a quiet person.

200
00:16:11,260 --> 00:16:12,565
It'd be great if we could

201
00:16:12,581 --> 00:16:13,885
