203
00:16:29,784 --> 00:16:30,656
Take it.

204
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:32,140
Nah, that's trash.

205
00:16:32,140 --> 00:16:34,300
That's your friend.

206
00:16:34,332 --> 00:16:35,532
Shut up.

207
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:39,280
There's one shot left!

208
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:40,560
