210
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:45,760
Yeah, I'm happy.

211
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:50,740
Hmm, what should I take a picture of?

212
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:55,880
Do you like taking photos?

213
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:59,140
Yeah. I wanted to be a photographer.

214
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:00,920
Then take some pictures.

215
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:03,580
Can I take a shot of you?

216
00:17:03,980 --> 00:17:05,080
Huh?

217
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:08,760
I'm sorry!

218
00:17:10,860 --> 00:17:12,020
Look at this!

219
00:17:18,344 --> 00:17:19,904
Hurry up.

220
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:21,452
There's only one shot left,

221
00:17:21,477 --> 00:17:23,093
so I'm going to take my time...

222
00:17:24,540 --> 00:17:25,660
Relax...

223
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:27,200
Smile.

224
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,400
Don't be ridiculous.

225
00:17:32,600 --> 00:17:34,420
Then talk to me about something.

226
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:37,480
- Talk?
- Yeah.

227
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:43,060
When did you start liking guys?

228
00:17:52,220 --> 00:17:54,150
I've always liked guys

229
00:17:54,175 --> 00:17:55,775
since I was little.

230
00:18:03,520 --> 00:18:05,293
When I was little,

231
00:18:05,722 --> 00:18:07,566
my parents took me to the hospital.

232
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,402
They said I was crazy

233
00:18:10,427 --> 00:18:12,107
and needed to be cured.

234
00:18:12,740 --> 00:18:14,280
That's when I decided.

235
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:16,141
I'd have to hide it

236
00:18:16,166 --> 00:18:17,846
for the rest of my life.

237
00:18:20,468 --> 00:18:21,657
So I avoided talking

238
00:18:21,673 --> 00:18:23,095
to anyone at school.

239
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,440
Ever been in a relationship?

240
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,420
Yeah.

241
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:32,680
Right after high school.

242
00:18:34,520 --> 00:18:35,820
Up until recently.

243
00:18:37,060 --> 00:18:38,280
What was his name?

244
00:18:40,540 --> 00:18:41,740
Shunichi.

245
00:18:42,620 --> 00:18:44,880
- Isn't this crazy?
- Teach me some English.

246
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:46,500
English? Sure, I'll teach you.

247
00:18:46,500 --> 00:18:47,740
- What about math?
- I barely passed.

248
00:18:47,740 --> 00:18:48,860
What score did you get in math?

249
00:18:48,860 --> 00:18:50,460
Wait a second, I'll go grab my stuff.

250
00:19:05,307 --> 00:19:06,347
Bye-bye.

251
00:19:08,456 --> 00:19:09,620
Bye-bye.

252
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:16,372
Even though I didn't talk to anyone,

253
00:19:16,397 --> 00:19:18,513
he came to say bye-bye to me

254
00:19:18,529 --> 00:19:19,740
before going home.

255
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:24,110
That was the extent of

256
00:19:24,134 --> 00:19:25,782
our relationship until graduation.

257
00:19:27,300 --> 00:19:32,540
But I still fell in love with Shunichi.

258
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:36,483
On graduation day,

259
00:19:37,155 --> 00:19:38,389
as I was about to leave

260
00:19:38,414 --> 00:19:40,064
